name: What is this, a crossover episode?

metadata.name: 20230220.wayfarer
metadata.description: I owe this entire collection to Tripgod.eth. He not only suggested its creation, but he's also been a huge supporter of my journey discovering how I create art. More than just art; I want to create a lasting resonating story. This first piece is based on an anime creation of his that he's never minted. I've taken it and leveraged AI generate what you see before your eyes. Where is she going? Where has she been? What lies ahead? Should we be more mindful of living in the present rather than falling into the trap of getting stuck in thought cycles about the past or future? How many licks does it take to get to the center of a tootsie pop? The world may never know...
